Nelisa, Big Brother Titans housemate has confirmed that she and Mmeli had sex. Nelisa made this known during a conversation with Blakboi, Miracle and Justin. She said she was sexually attracted to Mmeli and emotional at first. “We had a sexual relationship. We had sex. “I had a sexual attraction with Mmeli. I had an emotional attraction for him which led to a sexual attraction but I realized he just had a sexual attraction for me. She added that she is not over him sexually and emotionally. The duo fell out a week ago after it was alleged that they had sex. Mmeli appeared to have been avoiding Nelisa since the sexual encounter, prompting Yaya to confront him. Yaya had advised Mmeli that it was wrong to ignore Nelisa after their sexual encounters.